------+--------------+-----------+-----------+-------------+--------+----------+------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 emaj | next_version | f         | t         | f           | emaj   | {dblink} | E-Maj extension enables fine-grained write logging and time travel on subsets of the database.
